          },
          "code": "GET_CLEARING_ACCOUNT_INSIGHTS",
          "id": "1777998988020",
          "inputs": [
            {
              "id": "1777999007641_1",
              "name": "qParam",
              "value": "{{$context.$nodes.PREPARE_INSIGHT_SEARCH_FILTERS.$output.result}}",
              "required": true
            }
          ],
          "outputSpecification": "{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"items\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"insightRecipientId\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"insightSummary\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"recipientName\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"sensorSignal\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"signalId\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\"\n              },\n              \"policy\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\",\n                \"properties\": {\n                  \"ruleId\": {\n                    \"type\": \"string\"\n                  },\n                  \"ruleName\": {\n                    \"type\": \"string\"\n                  }\n                },\n                \"required\": [\n                  \"ruleId\",\n                  \"ruleName\"\n                ],\n                \"additionalProperties\": false\n              }\n            },\n            \"required\": [\n              \"signalId\",\n              \"policy\"\n            ],\n            \"additionalProperties\": false\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"insightRecipientId\",\n          \"insightSummary\",\n          \"recipientName\",\n          \"sensorSignal\"\n        ],\n        \"additionalProperties\": false\n      }\n    },\n    \"hasMore\": {\n      \"type\": \"boolean\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"required\": [\n    \"items\",\n    \"hasMore\"\n  ],\n  \"additionalProperties\": false\n}",
          "type": "BO_FUNCTION"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
            "name": "Organize Insight Results",
            "returnType": "object",
            "sourceCode": "let input = $context.$nodes.GET_CLEARING_ACCOUNT_INSIGHTS.$output;\n\nlet rulePriorityCodeLookup = $context.$variables.OraFUNRulePriority;\nlet categoryCodeLookup = $context.$variables.OraGLRuleCategory;\n\nconst map = new Map(\n    rulePriorityCodeLookup.map(item => [item.value, item])\n);\n\nconst categoryCodeLookupMap = new Map(\n    categoryCodeLookup.map(item => [item.value, item])\n);\n\nlet timeDifference = (creationDate) => {\n  const now = new Date();\n  const past = new Date(creationDate);\n\n  const diffInSeconds = Math.floor((now - past) / 1000);\n\n  const intervals = [\n    { label: \"day\", seconds: 86400 },\n    { label: \"hour\", seconds: 3600 },\n    { label: \"minute\", seconds: 60 }\n  ];\n\n  for (let i = 0; i < intervals.length; i++) {\n    const count = Math.floor(diffInSeconds / intervals[i].seconds);\n\n    if (count > 0) {\n      return count + \" \" + intervals[i].label + (count > 1 ? \"s ago\" : \" ago\");\n    }\n  }\n\n  return \"just now\";\n};\n\nlet items = (input?.items ?? []).map((row) => ({\n    insightRecipientId: row?.insightRecipientId,\n    ruleName: row?.sensorSignal?.policy?.ruleName,\n    insightSummary: row?.insightSummary,\n   // timeCreated: row?.timeCreated,\n    // timeCreatedMeaning: timeDifference(row?.timeCreated),\n    rulePriorityCode: row?.sensorSignal?.policy?.rulePriority?.lookupCode,\n//    bossFilter: row?.sensorSignal?.policy?.bossFilter,\n    rulePriorityCodeMeaning: row?.sensorSignal?.policy?.rulePriority?.meaning,\n    categoryCode: row?.sensorSignal?.policy?.categoryCode,\n    categoryCodeMeaning: categoryCodeLookupMap\n        ?.get(row?.sensorSignal?.policy?.categoryCode)\n        ?.label\n}));\n\nreturn { items };"
          },
          "outcomes": {
            "success": "1778060392959"
          },
          "diagram": {
            "x": 5450,
            "y": 7204
          },
          "code": "ORGANIZE_INSIGHT_RESULTS",
          "id": "1777999030321",
          "inputs": [],
          "outputSpecification": "{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"result\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\"\n    },\n    \"timeout\": {\n      \"type\": \"boolean\"\n    },\n    \"error\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"additionalProperties\": false,\n  \"required\": [\n    \"result\",\n    \"timeout\",\n    \"error\"\n  ]\n}",
          "type": "CODE"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
            "name": "Find Top Insights",
            "answerInUserLanguage": true
          },
          "outcomes": {
            "success": "1779094519444"
          },
          "diagram": {
            "x": 5450,
            "y": 7426
          },
          "code": "FIND_TOP_INSIGHTS",
          "id": "1778060392959",
          "inputs": [
            {
              "id": "1778060392960_1",
              "name": "prompt",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "You are specialized agent which will analyze and return array of insight objects. \n\n**INPUT**\n- Insight data: `{{$context.$nodes.ORGANIZE_INSIGHT_RESULTS.$output.result}}`\n\nEach object contains:\n- ruleName\n- insightSummary\n- rulePriorityCodeMeaning\n\n**DIRECTIVE**\n\nYour task is to:\n\n1. Transform `ruleName` into a user-friendly display label.\n   - Maximum 8-10 words\n   - Must preserve the financial meaning of the condition\n   - Must not introduce interpretation beyond what the condition states\n   - Convert technical/system-style names into readable business language.\n   - Add the transformed value as a new field called `displayRuleName`.\n   - Do NOT modify the original `ruleName`.\n   - never return data from below examples, only use these examples to transform the the `ruleName`\n   - Below are few examples:\n     Example - 1:\n     ruleName - Alert if the variance is > 15% between last period and current period for account Travel and Entertainment and company Fusion Napa\n     displayRuleName - Travel & Entertainment variance exceeds 15% MoM for Fusion Napa\n\n     Example - 2:\n     ruleName - asset clearing account 211347 balance >$1000 for company 3111 for last period\n     displayRuleName - Asset Clearing account unreconciled beyond 30 days\n     \n     Example - 3:\n     ruleName - Unapproved journals count >10 for current period \n     displayRuleName - More than 10 unapproved journals pending\n\n2. Analyze the `insightSummary` text and identify:\n   - primary financial figure from the narrative text\n   - if multiple figures are present, select the one representing total exposure or net variance or in similar financial terminology\n   - percentages\n   - counts\n   - numeric impact indicators\n   - risk/severity indicators\n   - trend direction (increase/decrease)\n   - urgency indicators\n\n3. Rank and sort the array based on overall business impact using:\n   - higher percentages\n   - larger counts\n   - stronger severity/risk wording\n   - higher priority values\n   - stronger negative or critical trends\n   - If there is no financial figure in insightSummary, assign rank = lowest (display last)\n3. If then input contains more than 5 items then Return ONLY the top 5 items based on rank\n4. Preserve the original objects exactly as they appear in the input.\n5. Do NOT modify, summarize, rewrite, rename, or remove any fields.\n6. Output must be a valid JSON array.\n\n**OUTPUT RULES**\n- Preserve all original fields exactly as provided.\n- Only add:\n  - `displayRuleName`\n  - `rank`\n- Do not summarize or rewrite the `insight`.\n- Do not remove any objects.\n- Return valid JSON array only.\n- No markdown.\n- No explanations."
            }
          ],
          "type": "LLM"
        },
        {
          "metadata": {
            "name": "Determine Display"
          },
          "outcomes": {
