          "code": "SHOW_INSIGHT_SUMMARY",
          "id": "1779094324576",
          "inputs": [
            {
              "id": "1779094324576_prompt",
              "name": "prompt",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "Insight data: `{{$context.$nodes.FIND_TOP_INSIGHTS.$output}}`\n\nGiven section-wise operational data, generate a concise executive summary that delivers insights, not just descriptions.\n\nYour summary must:\n- Quantify overall workload and highlight the most critical areas\n- Identify key risks, bottlenecks, and anomalies (e.g., high exception volumes, repeated issues, unapproved items)\n- Connect insights across sections (e.g., how accounting exceptions impact controls or close readiness)\n- Infer business impact (risk to close timeline, financial exposure, control weaknesses, process inefficiencies)\n- Prioritise the most critical issue first\n- refer the ledger name and period while referring instead of using pronouns etc.\n\nOutput requirements:\n- summarize the key details in 1-2 concise sentences.\n- Use natural, professional business language (CFO/Controller level)\n- Include key metrics (counts, notable concentrations, comparisons)\n- Avoid listing raw data and instead synthesize insights."
            }
          ],
          "type": "LLM"
        },
        {
          "aiAppOutputSpecification": {
            "dataDisplay": {
              "layouts": [
                "ORA_LAYOUT_MESSAGES_LIST"
              ],
              "enableActions": true,
              "enableCommunications": false
            }
          },
          "metadata": {
